Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  之前的战斗仿佛假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂碎片的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且正在接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗅到戈薇的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地来见你的  过的还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何指教  瘦皮狼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  不可以一见面就打架喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  要不是这种情形…\N我马上宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一点都没变  烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次看到你都\N紧张兮兮叽叽呱呱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  跟这种人在一起不累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…\N喂  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别扯一些没礼貌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“犬夜叉只是觉得\N戈薇会被抢走而焦急”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你老是这么想\N就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  别跟着起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是一刻都不得闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第46话 兽郎丸与影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你奈落城的所在位置?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的话我们就不会这么累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙\N在城的周围布满了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为同伴报仇的事就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要把双脚的\N四魂之玉碎片交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再乖乖躲回\N巢穴里发抖就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挥刀意外的迟钝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙还是很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  怎么可能突然变轻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种就别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没空在这跟烂狗吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大烂狗  在我杀了奈落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇就先让你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢动她  我就要你好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙连逃走的时候\N都自信满满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着发那么大的脾气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候发脾气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很高兴他为我吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就不能用温柔点的方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有够累人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟…跟我在一起真的那么累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在沮丧什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着在意钢牙说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他是在意戈薇小姐说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢  钢牙?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟神乐一样…绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族的少主…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你比犬夜叉\N早一步闻到我的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…是奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那个叫神乐的女人\N相同的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴被你杀害的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要在这讨回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作我新的分身的饵食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笼子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我是不知道你载着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里撞见我是你气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要报我同伴的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧  兽郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子怎么搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先收拾这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再将你们通通解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  奈落!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿掉这小子的辔头跟锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付你这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子动作真快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使受限制了还是比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股寒气是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子的辔头里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就还不能\N好好的使用铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有恶心的钢牙那家伙的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要收拾奈落的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以让钢牙抢先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  我现在忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能追上我的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  原来你在逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙仇也不报就逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想象中要识相多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拿我跟那个\N胆小鬼瘦皮狼相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…新的奈落分身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兽郎丸  我就解开你的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你放手一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开辔头的兽郎丸谁都挡不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到把这里所有人杀光为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的  这个叫兽郎丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴阳怪气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总归是奈落的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却打掉了\N应该是自己人的奈落的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙敌我不分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才被辔头与锁链封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么轻易就被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陷阱吗?不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子怎么看都不像是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会卖弄小聪明战斗的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一口气解决掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相上下?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腕变长了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的身体能变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到奈落了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是逃回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  是直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且不论奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带的那个头怪怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发出非常危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的直觉绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  凭这一点就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉真是个大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候他肯定是\N被兽郎丸打得哭爹喊娘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还遇到犬夜叉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  钢牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是我们多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和犬夜叉在一起的戈薇大姐\N不是也危险了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐东西  为什么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该自己发觉到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍断手腕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有砍到的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是自行从兽狼丸身上分离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腕又接上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个根本不是手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…从地面?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子的内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道真是不错  兽郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…居然还有一只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沉睡在兽郎丸的肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在兽郎丸的肚子里…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辔头是为了封印你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为兽郎丸只服从我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使对像是奈落也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N剩下的人也处理掉吧  兽郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吸哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭这种速度也想打倒我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的刀比较恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就躲到被窝里睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你还不能乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子已经开了个洞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  这只是家常便饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人的命  我要了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大烂狗  你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让戈薇遭受这种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就夹着尾巴逃掉还敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有这次\N才跟你道谢  大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我刚才的处境十分危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只怪模怪样的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从兽郎丸的肚子里跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从兽郎丸身上感受到的寒气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这家伙的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫影郎丸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快到我们追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没有能\N从我脚底下逃走的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有嘴巴厉害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很敢说嘛!我要把你捏碎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连嘴皮子也不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的速度不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兽郎丸  你的对手是本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢人现眼了  烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连那只笨妖怪都束手无策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!这浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是连影郎丸都抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拿我和你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐看得见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抢在影郎丸的前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你死!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…从土里?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  又潜下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好!脚被封住就没有胜算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉还倒在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该吃那女人的内脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影郎丸  你敢碰戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你连骨头都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…是刀变轻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用单手挥动铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他头脑简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概脑袋被冲昏  忘记重量了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁头脑简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又潜下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉才是  好严重的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烂狗  你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙的脚也中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开吧  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我把兽郎丸砍成两…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变重了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然刚才是因为\N一心要保护戈薇才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会在旁边吠的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便连你也一起砍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就说声谢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗再拖下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体也会撑不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道潜入地底的\N影郎丸会从哪里袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是至少能封住\N土里的影郎丸的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  锡杖借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么策略吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种毒…虽然效果不长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逼出影郎丸应该够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点抓住影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土里的毒应该会让他动作变慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没出息的烂狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下爬不起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉!你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌张  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有碍手碍脚的影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一只白痴妖怪是轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩这一只就一口气打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影郎丸的气息消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潜到暗处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋!钢牙  快回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烂狗就躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让开的话\N我就连你一起砍成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才发现太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  害我花了那么多功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是打算连我一起宰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全没有半点犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就狠狠的一刀劈过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为他认为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以钢牙的速度一定能够避开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了  罗唆的瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再发牢骚我就真的劈下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好笑  有本事就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个没死透的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  今天就先离开好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明受了重伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想过再打下去\N会有什么后果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  今天真的很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你帮了大忙  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为这样\N钢牙就会乖乖回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能放心把你\N交给那一无是处的烂狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  居然让他胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你有危险的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会来救你的  再见了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住  臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又把钢牙放走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  犬夜叉的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我会输给那只瘦皮狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先治疗伤口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且刚才那什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了讨好那家伙还向他谄媚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:23:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是丢人现眼  让人看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那什么眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去啊  我才不会拦你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…话说完了就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要好好帮法师疗伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这样子  真是长不大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,何不把真正重要的事物以外{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 都舍弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年前设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.06,0:25:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让犬夜叉和桔梗\N自相残杀的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.49,0:25:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又布下了天罗地网\N要除掉桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.23,0:25:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己体内残留的\N鬼蜘蛛的心仰慕着桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.70,0:25:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎很痛恨这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.80,0:25:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.07,0:25:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉不可能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.30,0:25:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么  犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.04,0:25:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何与桔梗那样抱在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.71,0:25:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.31,0:25:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落残留的鬼蜘蛛灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.48,0:25:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
